node.text:
We've got our hands on a pretty rare Suzuki Baleno Wagon, and we're giving it away to one of you! 😎

If you're a UK resident who's been having a hard time recently, and you could use a set of wheels to get you back up and going, send a message to the email in the video!

#carthrottle #cars #carsofinstagram #freecar #cheapcar #suzuki #baleno #suzukibaleno #carguys #cargirls #petrolhead

node.title: We're Giving Away A Rare Suzuki Baleno

node.text:
When we tried the new 992 Porsche 911 GT3 in Anglesey, we drove the Panamera Turbo S E-Hybrid to 'meet' it.

On paper these two seem very different. The Panamera uses a lot more shared parts from other VW Group cars, and it's around a tonne (!!) heavier. They're more alike than you'd think, though, and not just because they smell the same from the inside...

You get a real sense that the people who made them really give a damn about driving dynamics, and are better at chassis setup and feedback than pretty much everyone else.

It wouldn't be our Panamera of choice - we prefer the lighter, more nimble GTS - but the Turbo S E-Hybrid is a hugely impressive and very capable car. The acceleration is absurd, and since it now has a bigger battery, the electric range is decent.

The GT3 is pretty astonishing too, but you probably guessed that.

node.text:
Another amazing Legends Of The Autobahn show in the books!

From old school modified BMWs, to a fleet of Audi Quattros, and even a choice of not one, but two Mercedes SLR Roadsters! There were all sorts of cars on show today but one of our favorites has to be the white Alpina C2 2.7 you see in our recap video. You can't beat the retro Alpina stripes on a classic BMW!

node.text:
Yesterday's Quail Motorsports Gathering saw the public unveiling of a number of new cars. It's hard to boil it down to the best, but here are 3 of our favorites!

#MontereyCarWeek #MichelinMCW #TheQuail #Audi #Rimac #Pininfarina #Cars #Carsofinstagram #Petrolhead #Carguys #Cargirls

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Car Throttle on August 13, 2021. May be an image of car and road.

node.text:
Without a doubt one of our favorite spots so far at this year's Monterey Car Week has been the Radford Type 62-2 which was publicly unveiled today at The Quail.

If you're getting retro vibes from the Type 62-2, that's because the car is inspired by the 1960's Lotus Type 62 racecar. However the 62-2 gets a modern Lotus drivetrain to give it performance as well as looks. It features the 3.5-liter Toyota sourced V6, albeit supercharged to near 500hp! 

Radford itself is a coachbuilding company that helped develop the original GT40's bodywork back in the 60s. Despite closing its doors in 1966, the company has been given a new lease on life by a host of new backers, including car designer Mark Stubbs, former F1 champion Jenson Button, and fellow car nerd Ant Anstead.

With only 12 cars to be built, they'll be a rare sight to see! If you got an allocation for a Type 62-2, what would your spec/livery be? 🤔

#MontereyCarWeek #MichelinMCW #MichelinPilotSport #Radford #Radfordtype62 #Lotus #TheQuail #Cars #Carsofinstagram #Petrolhead #Carguys #Cargirls

node.text:
What an absolutely amazing day it has been at the Werks Reunion 2021!

If you like Porsches, this is the event for you. It's probably the only place on earth you'll see a daily driven 996 wearing the battle scars of 1000 parking lots proudly displayed next to a pristine showroom ready $300,000 993 Turbo S.

If 911s don't take your fancy, fear not, there's everything from an ultra rare Cayenne Transsyberia to one of the first Porsches ever made, a 1951 Porsche 356.

#MontereyCarWeek #MichelinMCW #Porsche #Werksreunion #Werksreunion2021 #Cars #Carsofinstagram #Petrolhead #Carguys #Cargirls

node.text:
The wheels of Werks!

Bonus points to anyone who can guess each car the wheels are from.

#MontereyCarWeek #MichelinMCW #Porsche #Werksreunion #Werksreunion2021 #Cars #Carsofinstagram #Petrolhead #Carguys #Cargirls

Who doesn't like a bit of AC Cobra to start their day 😍

We spotted this 289 roadster last night at the McCall's Motorworks Revival and couldn't help but get some shots of it. Do you prefer the look of the early narrow body street Cobras, or is it the angry wide stance of the later 427 cars for you?

#MontereyCarWeek #MichelinMCW #AC #ACcobra #Musclecar #Carguys #Cargirls #Petrolhead

node.text:
Welcome to Monterey Car Week 2021 presented by @michelinusa! We kicked it off last night at the epic 30th anniversary of the McCall's Motorworks Revival, where cars and planes come together in a spectacular fashion. What category of car do you want us cover most over the next few days? 🤔

#MontereyCarWeek #MichelinMCW #montereycarweek2021 #mccallsmotorworksrevival #mccalls #cars #carsofinstagram #supercars #hypercars #carguys #cargirls

Join us on Thursday the 12th for the beginning of the takeover!
